Package: WorldIPD
Type: Package
Title: Open Individual Participant Data (IPD) Hub
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mahmood", "Ahmad", email = "mahmood.ahmad2@nhs.net", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Scaffolding for the largest open IPD repository. Provides a standard schema, a registry of sources, fetchers for public datasets (Zenodo/GitHub/NHANES), validators, and a simple API to list and load datasets. All ingestion is read-only and provenance-first.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports: utils, stats, jsonlite
Suggests: httr, dplyr, tibble, readr
URL: https://github.com/mahmood789/WorldIPD
BugReports: https://github.com/mahmood789/WorldIPD/issues
